3 I want to transfer money from my Savings to Tahir	api_call:initial_slot_check, user_account:Savings, destination_name:Tahir

6 api_response:amount_check_api, api_result:success	confirm transaction ?

8 api_response:api_call, api_result:failed	end_call error in processing transaction

5 api_response:credit_debit_check_api, api_result:failed, message:'available options : debit'	It seems that you can't access that option, available options are : debit, would you like to change ?

1 <SILENCE>	how can i help you today ?
2 Can I see my transaction history ?	mem_call:transaction_history
3 Can I see my transaction history ?	api_call:request_accounts_api
4 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Savings	You have the following accounts : Savings , which one do you wish ?
5 Go for Savings	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
6 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:request_account_api
7 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Savings	You have the following accounts : Savings , which one do you wish ?
8 I want to use Savings account	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
9 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	which information should I give credit or debit ?
10 debit please	api_call:check_credit_debit_api, credit_debit:debit
11 api_response:credit_debit_check_api, api_result:success	can I ask what is the name of the partner ?
12 Vevake is the person you are looking for	api_call:destination_check_api, destination_name:Vevake
13 api_response:destination_check_api, api_result:failed, list_of_destination_names:Tahir	The recipient you provided is not registered, available list of recipients are : Tahir, would you like to change ?
14 accept	can I ask what is the name of the partner ?
15 Please use Samuel	api_call:destination_check_api, destination_name:Samuel
16 api_response:destination_check_api, api_result:failed, list_of_destination_names:Tahir	The recipient you provided is not registered, available list of recipients are : Tahir, would you like to change ?
17 reject	end_call User denied to change destination name

3 I would like to seem my transaction history from Savings	api_call:initial_slot_check_api, user_account:Savings
4 api_response:initial_slot_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:request_account_api
5 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Checkin,Credit,Savings	You have the following accounts : Checkin,Credit,Savings , which one do you wish ?
6 Savings account please	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
7 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	which information should I give credit or debit ?
8 Go for credit	api_call:check_credit_debit_api, credit_debit:credit
9 api_response:credit_debit_check_api, api_result:success	can I ask what is the name of the partner ?
10 I want it for Sourabh	api_call:destination_check_api, destination_name:Sourabh
11 api_response:destination_name_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:transaction_history_api, user_account:Savings, credit_debit:credit, destination_name:Sourabh
12 api_response:transaction_history_api, api_result:failed	end_call error in processing request !!

1 <SILENCE>	how can i help you today ?
2 I would like to seem my transaction history from Savings	mem_call:transaction_history
3 I would like to seem my transaction history from Savings	api_call:initial_slot_check_api, user_account:Savings
4 api_response:initial_slot_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:request_account_api
5 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Savings	You have the following accounts : Savings , which one do you wish ?
6 I want to use Savings account	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
7 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	which information should I give credit or debit ?
8 credit please	api_call:check_credit_debit_api, credit_debit:credit
9 api_response:credit_debit_check_api, api_result:failed, message:'available options : debit'	It seems that you can't access that option, available options are : debit, would you like to change ?
10 accept	which information should I give credit or debit ?
11 debit please	api_call:check_credit_debit_api, credit_debit:debit
12 api_response:credit_debit_check_api, api_result:success	can I ask what is the name of the partner ?
13 Tahir is the person	api_call:destination_check_api, destination_name:Tahir
14 api_response:destination_name_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:transaction_history_api, user_account:Savings, credit_debit:debit, destination_name:Tahir
15 api_response:transaction_history_api, api_result:success	end_call api_call successful !!

1 <SILENCE>	how can i help you today ?
2 I would like to see my credit transaction history from Credit to Vevake	mem_call:transaction_history
3 I would like to see my credit transaction history from Credit to Vevake	api_call:initial_slot_check_api, user_account:Credit, credit_debit:credit, destination_name:Vevake
4 api_response:initial_slot_check_api, api_result:failed, message:'one or more slots are faulty'	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Credit
5 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:failed, message:'available list of user accounts : Savings'	It seem's that user account you provided is invalid, your available user accounts are : Savings, would you like to change ?
6 accept	api_call:request_account_api
7 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Savings	You have the following accounts : Savings , which one do you wish ?
8 Go for Savings	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
9 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Credit
10 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:check_destination_name_api, destination_name:Vevake
11 api_response:destination_check_api, api_result:failed, list_of_destination_names:Marco,Matteo,Tahir	The recipient you provided is not registered, available list of recipients are : Marco,Matteo,Tahir, would you like to change ?
12 reject	end_call User denied to change destination name

1 <SILENCE>	how can i help you today ?
2 Can I see my transaction history ?	mem_call:transaction_history

5 I would like Credit account	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Credit
6 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:request_account_api
7 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Checkin,Credit,Savings	You have the following accounts : Checkin,Credit,Savings , which one do you wish ?
8 I want to use Savings account	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
9 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	which information should I give credit or debit ?
10 credit please	api_call:check_credit_debit_api, credit_debit:credit
11 api_response:credit_debit_check_api, api_result:success	can I ask what is the name of the partner ?
12 Tahir is the person	api_call:destination_check_api, destination_name:Tahir
13 api_response:destination_check_api, api_result:failed, list_of_destination_names:Marco,Matteo,Simone,Vevake	The recipient you provided is not registered, available list of recipients are : Marco,Matteo,Simone,Vevake, would you like to change ?
14 reject	end_call User denied to change destination name

1 <SILENCE>	how can i help you today ?
2 Can I see my transaction history ?	mem_call:transaction_history
3 Can I see my transaction history ?	api_call:request_accounts_api
4 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Checkin,Savings	You have the following accounts : Checkin,Savings , which one do you wish ?
5 Go for Savings	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
6 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:request_account_api
7 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Checkin,Savings	You have the following accounts : Checkin,Savings , which one do you wish ?
8 Savings account please	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
9 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	which information should I give credit or debit ?
10 prefer to use debit	api_call:check_credit_debit_api, credit_debit:debit
11 api_response:credit_debit_check_api, api_result:success	can I ask what is the name of the partner ?
12 It is Serra	api_call:destination_check_api, destination_name:Serra
13 api_response:destination_name_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:transaction_history_api, user_account:Savings, credit_debit:debit, destination_name:Serra
14 api_response:transaction_history_api, api_result:failed	end_call error in processing request !!

5 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:failed, message:'available list of user accounts : Credit'	It seem's that user account you provided is invalid, your available user accounts are : Credit, would you like to change ?

8 I would like Credit account	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Credit
9 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Checkin
10 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:credit_debit_check_api, credit_debit:credit

12 reject	end_call you denied to change the option

1 <SILENCE>	how can i help you today ?
2 Can I see my transaction history ?	mem_call:transaction_history
3 Can I see my transaction history ?	api_call:request_accounts_api
4 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Savings	You have the following accounts : Savings , which one do you wish ?
5 Savings account please	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
6 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:request_account_api
7 api_response:request_account_api, list_of_accounts: Savings	You have the following accounts : Savings , which one do you wish ?
8 Please use Savings account	api_call:check_account_api, user_account:Savings
9 api_response:account_check_api, api_result:success	which information should I give credit or debit ?
10 Go for debit	api_call:check_credit_debit_api, credit_debit:debit
11 api_response:credit_debit_check_api, api_result:success	can I ask what is the name of the partner ?
12 It is Simone	api_call:destination_check_api, destination_name:Simone
13 api_response:destination_name_check_api, api_result:success	api_call:transaction_history_api, user_account:Savings, credit_debit:debit, destination_name:Simone
14 api_response:transaction_history_api, api_result:failed	end_call error in processing request !!
